cxt = self.spring.context
obj = cxt.get_object(obj_id)
assert obj is not None
assert obj.message == message
pytest.mark.parametrize('obj_id, message', [('TestObjectYAML',
    'This is a test message that is set by spring via YAML config'), (
    'TestObject',
    'This is a test message that is set by spring via Object context')])
